text: Jangal Mariala railway station (Urdu and ) is located in Jangal Mariala village, Khanewal district of Punjab province of the Pakistan. ==See also== * List of railway stations in Pakistan * Pakistan Railways ==References== ==External links== *Official Web Site of Pakistan Railways Category:Railway stations in Punjab, Pakistan Category:Railway stations on Lodhran–Khanewal Branch Line
